{"type":"message","id":"317e4c0d","parentId":"83944e70","timestamp":"2026-03-28T05:28:45.016Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The document has been successfully updated. Let me summarize what was done.","thinkingSignature":"eaf166a37490f4882a186bd2457182f91ae58a4bf0eba07029fe10c094b3dd91"},{"type":"text","text":"搞定啦！文档已全部更新，主要改动如下：\n\n**1. 项目标题改为可点击链接**\n每个项目的标题现在都是 Markdown 链接格式，点击标题即可跳转到对应 GitHub 仓库：\n\n```\n## 🔬 项目一：[mvanhorn/last30days-skill](https://github.com/mvanhorn/last30days-skill)\n```\n\n**2. 每个项目加入「仓库地址」字段**\n每个项目标题下方新增了醒目的仓库地址行：\n\n```\n**仓库地址：** https://github.com/mvanhorn/last30days-skill\n```\n\n**3. 精简基础信息表**\n原来的 4 列表格（项目名称、GitHub 地址、总⭐、今日⭐）替换为简洁的一行信息，包含仓库地址和 star 数据，避免了重复。\n\n现在 9 个项目的标题都变成了可点击的链接，阅读调研文档时可以直接跳转到对应仓库啦 🦐"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed","usage":{"input":32347,"output":203,"cacheRead":37026,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69576,"cost":{"input":0.0194082,"output":0.00048719999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0022215599999999996,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02211696}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774675718448}}
